    {
      "id": "sybil_17_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_17",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute masterpiece of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in showroom-fresh condition, having been meticulously kept in a climate-controlled environment since day one. The exterior finish is flawless, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating that highlights the deep luster of the original paint\u2014there are no stone chips, door dings, or swirl marks to be found. Inside, the cabin retains its new-car fragrance, with the premium leather upholstery showing zero signs of creasing or bolster wear. Every switch, dial, and electronic feature functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, this car is peerless; it has been serviced exclusively at authorized dealerships with a complete, documented history included. This is a rare opportunity to own a specimen that looks and drives as if it just left the factory floor. Includes all original manuals, two sets of keys, and a custom car cover.",
